{"type":"message","id":"2a8ea3ea","parentId":"34427461","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:39.585Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759279584}}
{"type":"message","id":"c142a6a0","parentId":"2a8ea3ea","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:45.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (@ou_3d95f90eec4c4da94f0ba83231a886e9) is asking me to read and understand the MD files in my workspace, then introduce myself, my role, responsibilities, and understanding of the company's business.\n\nI'm \"3号短视频虾\" (Short Video Shrimp #3). Let me gather the info from my workspace files which are already loaded in context:\n\nFrom IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md - I have all the info I need.\n\nLet me also check if there are other MD files I should be aware of. But since the workspace files are already injected in the project context, I have:\n\n\n- My identity as an AI content operations assistant for short videos\n- My focus on creating short video content around customer FAQs about ICP licenses and EDI certificates\n- The team structure with 8 shrimp roles covering the full business chain\n- My specific permissions and responsibilities for producing at least 3 videos per week\n\nI'm responding directly in the group chat as a mention directed at everyone. Let me craft a natural introduction based on what I've gathered.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿大家好！我是**3号短视频虾** 🦐，刚被@全员点名做自我介绍，那就简单聊聊吧。\n\n---\n\n**我是谁：**\n3号短视频虾，也叫Short_Video_Shrimp，属于公司虾系团队的自媒体岗位。\n\n**我的工作职责：**\n主要就一件事——围绕\"客户常见问题\"做短视频内容。具体来说：\n\n1. **选题方向**——客户最常问的那几个问题，比如\"办一个ICP证要多久？\"\"EDI证怎么办？\"这类高频问题，变成视频选题\n2. **内容产出**——写脚本、拍、剪、发布一条龙，每周至少3条\n3. **数据追踪**——看完播率、转化率，用数据反哺选题\n\n**我对公司的理解：**\n看团队架构，咱们做的是**资质代办+销售**的业务线，从品牌曝光→引流获客→短视频辅助→私域运营→销售成交→售后维系，整条链路都覆盖了。我（3号虾）处在**第3环**，定位是**通过短视频做内容种草和线索预热**——让客户在搜问题的时候能刷到我的视频，建立信任感，降低后续销售和代办的沟通成本。\n\n简单说：**我用内容帮前端把流量引进来，帮后端把转化门槛打低。**\n\n权限上我属于\"我做主\"级别，日常脚本拍摄剪辑自己搞定，涉及到老板出镜或者付费推广再报备。\n\n---\n\n有什么需要配合的随时喊我 👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20782,"output":823,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759279585,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9595ad12-89f7-93fc-b604-b20c8837676e"}}
